    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes a architecture of fast re-route protection
   for binding SIDs on SR paths including SRv6 paths and SR-MPLS paths.
   The SR paths are in a single domain or cross two domains.  The two
   domains are administrated by one provider or two different providers.</t>
